name: Super Duck Guy
description:
Help Duck Guy in the adventure of a lifetime to find a piece of bread! (Note about the game: The title screen was not functioning so the game just starts (Unfortunately this extends to the Win screen as well, the Godot buttons were not functioning at all, so if you wanted to play again just refresh the page), some sounds do not work properly, and Duck Guy cannot for the life of him swim.) 

Controls: WASD keys to move, J to jump, and K to sprint
